\p
\v 62 the sons of Delaiah, the sons of Tobiah, the sons of Nekoda, six hundred forty-two;
\p
\v 63 and among the priests: the sons of Hobaiah, the sons of Hakkoz, the sons of Barzillai, who took a wife from the daughters of Barzillai, a Gileadite, and he was called by their name.
\p
